'''Cody Lightning''' (born August 8, 1986) is a [[Plains Cree|Cree]] [[Native Americans in the United States|Native American]] [[actor]].
He is son of [[Georgina Lightning]], and brother of William Lightning and [[Crystle Lightning]].<ref>http://www.nativecelebs.com/profiles/cody_lightning.htm NativeCelebs</ref>
Nominated for the Young Artist Award in 1999 for Best Performance in a Feature Film - Supporting Young Actor, for ''[[Smoke Signals (film)|Smoke Signals]]'' (1998).<ref>https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0120321/ IMDB</ref>
Won [[American Indian Film Festival]] Movie Award in 2007 for Best Actor in ''[[Four Sheets to the Wind]]'' (2007).<ref>https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0893331/ IMDB</ref>
